<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.8.1">
<l>ceṅkamalat tirumakaḷum puviyuñ cempoṉ tiruvaṭiyi ṉiṇaivaruṭa muṉiva rētta</l>
<l>vaṅkamali taṭaṅkaṭalu ḷaṉanta ṉeṉṉum variyaravi ṉaṇaittuyiṉṟa māyōṉ kāṇmiṉ</l>
<l>eṅkumali niṟaipukaḻnāl vēta maintu vēḷvikaḷuṅ kēḷvikaḷu miyaṉṟa taṉmai</l>
<l>yaṅkamalat tayaṉaṉaiyār payiluñ celvat taṇiyaḻuntūr niṉṟukanta vamarar kōvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Māyōṉ who sleeps on a bed [that is] a striped serpent called, “Ananta,”</l>
<l rend="indent">in the wide sea where waves swell as sages praise [him],</l>
<l>While lady Tiru of the red lotus and the earth [goddess]</l>
<l rend="indent">stroke both his fine golden feet,</l>
<l>Behold, is the king of immortals who is happy</l>
<l rend="indent">standing in lovely, prosperous Aḻuntūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">where dwell those like the Unborn on the beautiful lotus,</l>
<l>Whose nature is suited to the four Vedas,</l>
<l rend="indent">whose full glory abounds everywhere, the five sacrifices,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the revelations.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
